com.logitopia.jmortar.core.sort

Interface Sort<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of item that we wish to sort.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BubbleSort, ParallelMergeSort, SelectionSort

    public interface Sort<T>
    Sort the given list, using the given comparator. The comparator will validate whether or not two components are in the expected position, relative to each other.
